>\n遲D拆9佢地十字架，換習像上去，佢地都會話「尊敬國家領導人係常態」"},{"pid":"f078bed842d9d06a873b7ea13506ba5c8cb3f120","tid":468021,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:01:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時將個首都擺喺江西瑞金啊？</blockquote><br />\n習家龍興之地係延安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558f03955b0cfe99d9ac5f39916c6c44c07e3a07","tid":468021,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:03:13.000Z","msg":"文革2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690de01c85c6b341709d765aad70c3e8f6dbcbc4","tid":468021,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:04:47.000Z","msg":"好似北韓"},{"pid":"902f95e455e38ffa8b775b5ca8dcc3d2a056ddee","tid":468021,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:08:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文革2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n文革呢啲活動係應該每隔七八年搞一次㗎嘛,如果雜種要搞文革我諗冇乜邊個x登仔會反對"},{"pid":"a331351593d65b5fa2a4b7b3f91b2e70419f1aed","tid":468021,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:08:51.000Z","msg":"其實信習近平仲實際過信耶穌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49dae205df9ca41ac291c96a671fea437ec75e99","tid":468021,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>越獨裁越好 物極必反</blockquote><br />\n建設民主中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7e9c79d139b4838205104c0d449bdd5227ce5e","tid":468021,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:09:32.000Z","msg":"幾時有生祠？想去裝柱香"}]}